Remy Auberjonois https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Remy_Auberjonois 0 Remy-Luc Auberjonois (born January 21, 1974) is an American actor. Auberjonois is best known for his recurring role as Mr. Albin in the television series Weeds and as Dr Emerson on the television series Mad Men.
